.IX Title "Pod::Readme::Plugin::requires 3"
.TH Pod::Readme::Plugin::requires 3 "2018-10-31" "perl v5.28.2" "User Contributed Perl Documentation"
.\" For nroff, turn off justification.  Always turn off hyphenation; it makes
